    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>In nomine Dei, amen. <persName key="#Emperor/king" ref="#people/21"
                            >Berengarius</persName> Romanorum <rs key="#Emperor/king">imperator</rs>
                        semper augustus &amp;c. Tibi <persName key="#Marquis/duke"><name
                                ref="Uguccio">Uguccioni</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Marquis/duke">marchioni de Colle</rs> filio olim <persName
                            key="#Marquis/duke"><name ref="Uguccio">Uguccionis</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Marquis/duke">marchionis de Tuscia</rs> et tuis posteris perpetuam
                        auctoritatem concedimus atque donamus in nobile feudum infrascripta oppida
                        et <rs key="#Uncertain_tradition #Castle">castra</rs> cum eorum <rs
                            key="#Curtes">curtibus</rs>, territoriis omnibus et rebus, videlicet <rs
                            key="#Castle">castrum Collis</rs>, <rs key="#Castle">castrum
                            Civitellae</rs>, <rs key="#Castle">castrum Vernae</rs>, <rs
                            key="#Castle">castrum Pierlis</rs>, <rs key="#Castle">castrum
                            Passignani</rs>, <rs key="#Castle">castrum Gherardum</rs>, <rs
                            key="#Castle">castrum Metrelli</rs>, et <rs key="#Castle">castrum
                            Favalti</rs> cum tota sua <rs key="#Mountains">montanea</rs>, <rs
                            key="#Mountains">Montis Bruni</rs>, <rs key="#Castle">castrum Montis
                            Erculis</rs>, <rs key="#Castle">castrum Cisteinae</rs>, <rs
                            key="#Castle">castrum Monticellae</rs>, <rs key="#Castle">castrum
                            Castiglionis</rs>, et <rs key="#Castle">Cetonae</rs>, <rs key="#Castle"
                            >castrum Ciciani</rs>, <rs key="#Castle">castrum <rs key="#Marquis/duke"
                                >marchionum</rs>
                            <placeName ref="#places/505">civitatis Aretii</placeName></rs>, <rs
                            key="#Castle">castrum Lugnani</rs>, <rs key="#Castle">castrum
                            Mirani</rs>, et <rs key="#Castle">castrum Proggi</rs>. Te tuosque
                        posteros in perpetuum nostros milites facimus et imperii ab omnibus oneribus
                        vos et vestras terras liberamus in perpetuum, et quod bona vestra possitis
                        semper recuperare nulla praescriptione contradicente, sed non alienare etiam
                        in praecepto imperatoris et regis Romanorum. Et si ulla persona contrafuerit
                        in aliquo huic privilegio, in poena ultimi supplicii puniatur. Et
                        praecipimus quod dictum privilegium sit sigillatum more imperatoris. Datum
                        Romae anno Domini noningentesimo decimo septimo, indictione V, quinto
                        kalendas iulii, anno imperii primo. Locus signi Berengerii serenissimi
                        Romanorum imperatoris. Et ego Vitalis cancellarius dictum privilegium
                        sigillavi, qui Berengerius sic precepit dictis testibus &amp;c.</ab>
                </div>
